<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.4.2">
<l>vaiya muṇṭā lilaimē vumāyaṉ maṇinīṇmuṭi</l>
<l>paikoḷ nākat taṇaiyāṉ payilu miṭameṉparāl</l>
<l>taiyal nallār kuḻalmā laiyummaṟ ṟavartaṭamulai</l>
<l>ceyya cāntuṅ kalantiḻi puṉalcūḻ teṉṉaraṅkamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They truly say that the place where abides the one whose couch</l>
<l rend="indent">is a serpent with hoods,</l>
<l>[The one] with a high jeweled crown, Māyaṉ who dwells on a banyan leaf,</l>
<l rend="indent">having consumed the world,</l>
<l>Is Araṅkam of the South encircled by water where flows</l>
<l rend="indent">and mixes fine sandalwood paste</l>
<l>From the broad bosoms of beautiful women,</l>
<l rend="indent">as well as the garlands in their curls.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
